        "subject": "LU-12021 mdt: make useless error message a debug one",
        "message": "LU-12021 mdt: make useless error message a debug one\n\nWhen there are unknown flags in mdt_attr_valid_xlate(),\nthere are simply ignored but an error message is printed.\nAs they are ignored and nothing is wrong most of time, avoid\nfilling the kernel log with these useless warnings.\nReplace CERROR with a CDEBUG.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Aurelien Degremont <degremoa@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Ic8f9c53fa65d030e95505f20a327b8d26545f2a6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
